reviewText: Salzburg one of my favourite cities what a pleasure to see this video having visited on numerous occasions. I wish  was here for the New year,
Very little useful content and annoying music.

Sometimes it sounds less like an actual songs you would hear on the radio (europe), and more like a 15s ringtone constantly looped.

Its nice to see areas i haven't been to in a while, but i would have liked longer "shots".
This isn't an action movie and doesn't need a cut to a different image every 10s.
Music is annoying. Pics were so similar.
The music was beautiful and the sights were stunning. This is a nice background to put on for a party.
